INSTALL

1. Download crack:
   $ cd [dir_for_crack]
   $ git clone git@github.com:RemiBe/Crack.git

2. Add [dir_for_crack] to a .pth file
   in $HOME/.local/lib/python[your_python_version]/site-packages/[filename].pth
   (create the directories if they do not exist, any filename works).

   NB: Crack is implemented in Python 3.

3. Test it!
   $ cd [dir_for_crack]/crack/main
   $ python crack_part.py examples/mushroom.yaml
   Which just initializes a mesh.

